snippet.title: CAT RESCUE STORY | ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER
snippet.description:
Take over the shelter, bring in rescue cats, discover their quirks, care for them, and find them the perfect home in Cat Rescue Story. Renovate, decorate, and make more room for even more cats! 

Cat Rescue Story is coming to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and PC on September 26th.
